data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Mustang, Oklahoma! Large bedrooms in this 1670 SF home with a wrap around master closet! 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home has a large living area with cathedral ceilings and a spacious kitchen which is great for holiday or football get-togethers or entertaining! Large kitchen pantry. Nest Thermostat to control heat/air when away from home.  Step on to the brand new LVP flooring or enjoy the feel of the new luxury carpet in the bedrooms. French doors that open to the back covered patio.  Only 8 minutes to the Kilpatrick Turnpike, making it easy access to the Oklahoma City Metro within minutes.  Refrigerator stays with acceptable offer.
